import axios from "axios"; import { useEffect } from "react"; import { Table } from "react-bootstrap-icons"; import { useDispatch, useSelector } from "react-redux" import { fillData } from "../slice/sliceContact"; function Contacts() { const localStore = useSelector((state) => { return state }) const dispach = useDispatch() const getData = async () => { const response = await axios.get('http://localhost:5000/contact') dispach(fillData(response.data)) } useEffect(() => { getData() }, []) console.log(localStore); return <>
# First Name Last Name Username
1 Mark Otto @mdo
2 Jacob Thornton @fat
3 Larry the Bird @twitter
} export default Contacts
